  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/1328738/" class="title-link">男人这东西是什么东西呢？</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-1328738"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/shouzhu/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u2225410-2.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/shouzhu/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">瘦竹</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar50 main-title-rating" title="力荐"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2008-03-17"
      class="main-meta">2008-03-17 18:45:42</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_1328738_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                    日本作家渡边淳一(对，就是那个让一个男人和一个女人死在《失乐园》的家伙)，还写过一本不太有名的书《男人这东西》，他用这本薄薄的书轻轻挑开了男人仅剩的一个小裤头，让男人的双手不知是该先挡住自己的脸，还是先挡住自己的私处。他这样做我想并不是为了进行一次恶作剧，...

                    <a class="pl" href="https://book.douban.com/review/1328738/#comments">(46回应)</a>
                  <div class="more-info pl clearfix">
                    <span class="left">118有用 / 28没用</span>
                  </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div id="review_1328738_full" class="hidden">
            <div id="review_1328738_full_content" class="full-content"></div>
          </div>
        </div>
    </div>
  </div>

      
  



