  <h2>谁读这本书?</h2>
  <div class="indent" id="collector">

    

<div class="">
    
    <div class="ll"><a href="https://www.douban.com/people/141107487/"><img src="https://img1.doubanio.com/icon/u141107487-9.jpg" class="pil" alt="费株株" /></a></div>
    <div style="padding-left:60px"><a class="" href="https://www.douban.com/people/141107487/">费株株</a><br/>
      <div class="pl ll">          1小时前          读过      </div>

        <span class="allstar40" title="推荐"></span>
      <br/>


    </div>
    <div class="clear"></div><br/>
    <div class="ul" style="margin-bottom:12px;"></div>
</div>
<div class="">
    
    <div class="ll"><a href="https://www.douban.com/people/153244983/"><img src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u153244983-2.jpg" class="pil" alt="Lucky麦_" /></a></div>
    <div style="padding-left:60px"><a class="" href="https://www.douban.com/people/153244983/">Lucky麦_</a><br/>
      <div class="pl ll">          今天下午          想读      </div>

      <br/>

      <span class="pl">tags:两性 心理学</span><br />

    </div>
    <div class="clear"></div><br/>
    <div class="ul" style="margin-bottom:12px;"></div>
</div>
<div class="">
    
    <div class="ll"><a href="https://www.douban.com/people/150121352/"><img src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u150121352-1.jpg" class="pil" alt="Carol" /></a></div>
    <div style="padding-left:60px"><a class="" href="https://www.douban.com/people/150121352/">Carol</a><br/>
      <div class="pl ll">          今天下午          读过      </div>

        <span class="allstar40" title="推荐"></span>
      <br/>


          <span class="">作者站在一个不考虑道德的立场，剖析了男人内心的卑劣性。撕开面具和伪装，那些男人们可能不想承认的部分的确可以解释很多事情，我可以理解但是也更加无奈和悲观。</span> <br/>
    </div>
    <div class="clear"></div><br/>
    <div class="ul" style="margin-bottom:12px;"></div>
